title: Unknown Songwriters – Catapult Support
meta_description: While you should make every effort to submit and properly credit the full name of the actual Songwriter for every track that you submit,...
main_content: Articles in this section Real Names for Songwriters Unknown Songwriters While you should make every effort to submit and properly credit the full name of the actual Songwriter for every track that you submit, we realize this is not always possible.* If the unknown Songwriter for a given track is for a very old, archaic or traditional song (ie: Historical chants, traditional folk songs, etc.) when you submit the Songwriter/Composer name you can click on "I don't know the songwriter / composer" as shown below: You NEVER submit a songwriter name as "Public Domain, "DAR", etc. as this makes literally no sense. *The majority of your album's tracks must have a known songwriter. We will not distribute an album if the majority of the songwriters are unknown by you. Related articles Real Names for Songwriters How Long Does It Take for My Music to Get into the Music Stores? Compound Artist Names are Prohibited Additional Contributors What is Spotify for Artists?
